POE-Component-Player-Slideshow version 1.4
===========================================

This module provies a POE wrapper for the quiv application, allowing
developers to write Perl applications that remote-control this 
slideshow viewer.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

1. the POE state engine
2. the PoCo::Child component
3. the X11::SendEvent module
4. the "qiv" application
5. XFree86 :)

ACKNOWLEDGEMENTS

